fields.Title: COAST ORB / arno van eyck after
fields.Description: Afterthought reaction orbital to those flyers, man. Do it. Talk to your stupid brain.

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "Cold drops of rain fall onto your o..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Cold drops of rain fall onto your outstretched hand. A slight tremble passes through it...

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "Large flakes of snow fall onto your..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Large flakes of snow fall onto your outstretched hand. A slight tremble passes through it...

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "He nods. "Let's get going. We have..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He nods. "Let's get going. We have a case to solve."

fields.Title: Endurance: "Yes. It's likely triggered by a foc..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Yes. It's likely triggered by a focal epileptic seizure in your temporal lobe.

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "...and is swept away, out of existe..."
fields.Dialogue Text: ...and is swept away, out of existence.

fields.Title: You: "Did that really happen just now?"
fields.Dialogue Text: Did that really happen just now?

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Okay. Well. I'm not going to ask w..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Okay. Well. I'm not going to ask who Van Eyck is. I'm just going to assume it's your business and move on, okay?" He raises his collar.

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "Your outstretched hand basks in the..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Your outstretched hand basks in the warm spring sun.

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "At the back of your head you feel t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: At the back of your head you feel the rapid beat of anodic music... then it fades away.

fields.Title: You: "Grab it quickly."
fields.Dialogue Text: Grab it quickly.

fields.Title: You: "[Ignore thought.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: [Ignore thought.]

fields.Title: You: "Am I hallucinating?"
fields.Dialogue Text: Am I hallucinating?

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "And so all our lives become but a f..."
fields.Dialogue Text: And so all our lives become but a faded memory, an ephemeral vision of a Van Eyck concert flyer... blink or you'll miss it.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "The lieutenant is looking at the sp..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The lieutenant is looking at the spot you were reaching for. "Did you notice something important?"

fields.Title: You: "Okay, I'm done with this. [Finish t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Okay, I'm done with this. [Finish thought.]

fields.Title: Endurance: "Yeah, probably, one day. But not th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Yeah, probably, one day. But not this very minute.

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "Things in the night are not what th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Things in the night are not what they seem to be...

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "As your hand reaches for the small..."
fields.Dialogue Text: As your hand reaches for the small rectangle of glossy paper, it snaps free from the branch...

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "The shadows play tricks on your min..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The shadows play tricks on your mind...

fields.Title: You: ""No... I don't think so. It was jus..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "No... I don't think so. It was just a reflection or something. Never mind."

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "One of the flyers has gotten stuck..."
fields.Dialogue Text: One of the flyers has gotten stuck to the branches of a small brush. The sound of it flapping in the wind is an echo of Van Eyck.

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "Your outstretched hand casts a deep..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Your outstretched hand casts a deep shadow on the ground...

fields.Title: You: "Is it dangerous?"
fields.Dialogue Text: Is it dangerous?

fields.Title: Endurance: "I don't know... probably. I'm not a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: I don't know... probably. I'm not a doctor.

fields.Title: You: ""Never mind. Let's get going." [Fin..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Never mind. Let's get going." [Finish thought.]

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "Flakes of snow fall onto your outst..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Flakes of snow fall onto your outstretched hand. A slight tremble passes through it...

fields.Title: You: "Oh my god, I'm going to die!"
fields.Dialogue Text: Oh my god, I'm going to die!

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "No."
fields.Dialogue Text: No.

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "Cold drops of rain fall onto your o..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Cold drops of rain fall onto your outstretched hand. A slight tremble passes through it...

fields.Title: Shivers: "IT HAPPENED ONCE; LONG AGO"
fields.Dialogue Text: IT HAPPENED ONCE; LONG AGO

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "In the back of your head, you feel..."
fields.Dialogue Text: In the back of your head, you feel the rapid beat of anodic music... then it fades away.

fields.Title: You: "What the shit?"
fields.Dialogue Text: What the shit?

fields.Title: You: ""Kim, I think I'm seeing Van Eyck p..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Kim, I think I'm seeing Van Eyck posters everywhere now."

fields.Title: Shivers: "A GLIMPSE INTO THE PAST"
fields.Dialogue Text: A GLIMPSE INTO THE PAST
